  "texts": [
    "For instance, in Fig. 5a, Mean Diastolic blood pressure was defined as a sub-tag of Patient Characteristics.",
    "The user can also visualise the resulting taxonomy as a radial tree chart, as shown in Fig. 5b.",
    "In this section, we describe the four tools that support the extraction phase (Dextr, ExaCT, Iris.ai, and RobotReviewer/RobotSearch) with a focus on the six AI features relevant to the extraction phase.",
